        body: 'Identity and Access Management gives the right permissions to the right people at the right time. Every entity — human and non-human — gets a digital identity. IAM covers identity proofing, provisioning, permission assignment, authentication, authorization, and governance. SSO reduces credential fatigue; LDAP, SAML, and OAuth enable protocol-level interoperability; federation extends access to partner organizations.',
